snippet.title: Aliens Attack Arcade Video Game
snippet.description:
Aliens Attack is a 9 levels shooter Arcade video game. Winning each level is challenging and Adrenaline Booster. The game is enjoyable and will make you fun. Winning a level is simple: Kill enemies, and escape from bullets and obstacles.

Play on Itch:
- Itch
https://excitedgames.itch.io/aliens-attack

Download from Kartridge:
